{"tid":424076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(因...) 快運CEO傳孭鑊下台","createTime":"2017-10-04T11:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T11:58:49.000Z","uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d34e6158c7d984699bdd51f33a5642e3a85e37f5","tid":424076,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"香港快運在毫無預告下於十一長假期突然取消18班航機，造成旅客大恐慌，快運內部管理及行政混亂浮現，快運高層早前更就事件致歉。今天(4日)有消息指，快運行政總裁安浩恩(Andrew Cowen)與另外2名高層已經離職。&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有外電報道指，有2名消息人士證實安浩恩離職的消息，離職原因與近期取消航班事件，以及培訓人員離職事件有關，另外，有2名高層將會跟隨離職。另有報道則指，安浩恩未有承認離職的消息，僅稱公司即將發出聲明，有指他其實是調任其他崗位，但亦有指他不願降職而選擇離開快運。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另有消息指，快運的人才培養及創新總經理Christopher Thomas已調職，其職位由香港航空人力資源及行政總監Stanley Yau頂替。&nbsp;<br />\nOncc 東網報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b323f56f824995da4fa36b4568a03e4acf5f7eb2","tid":424076,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"HX人管UO<br />\n咁UO發展會唔會受限制？<br />\n特別係同HX overlap 嘅航線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a2a730ed133dea4fe2871cc2b8425ec4f27258","tid":424076,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6317dc2e56cadbccb03c641f24444aeb050c5a","tid":424076,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"你估真係佢渣旗咩<br />\n佢自己都唔想做啦"},{"pid":"36fdcc1641be36c65f568738a4c2b57c452fa1a2","tid":424076,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"又開香檳喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cathaypacific.com/content/dam/cx/digital-library/hk/press-release/archived/20100401_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%